														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1696489">
									

<p>Yet this is simply answering the question that is created by the context of this canon: &quot;If the Foundation isn't containing these things, then what happened with them?&quot; I know that I for one want to know, and thus I find all these entries to be excellent.</p>
<p>I will say that it's moderately annoying to include Iris specifically, but then I've never been a big fan of her anyway and felt she was way overused. Still worth the read.</p>

							</div>

								
					
